
We listen to event transmission packets, and then wait for the event to be 
transmitted with the old requested sequence number


eventrxdecode:

Decodes the events transmitted by the network
interface. At the moment we are just transmitting timestamps from timer, 
so we extract out the event sequence ID and the timestamp. 


retxreq_inst: 

Requests a retransmission when RETXREQREQ is asserted

